OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOil prices remain over $100 a barrel
OL,8,Fmark as the US-Israeli war in Iran
OL,9,Fends its third week, despite pleas
OL,10,Ffrom global leaders for the regime to
OL,11,Funblock the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FIran has effectively closed the
OL,14,Fwaterway - which a fifth of the
OL,15,Fworld's oil typically sails through -
OL,16,Fcausing huge up and down swings to the
OL,17,Ffinancial market and soaring
OL,18,Fpredictions for household bills in the
OL,19,FUK this summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
