OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMore than 30 countries agreed on March
OL,8,F11 to release a record 400 million
OL,9,Fbarrels of reserve oil to combat
OL,10,Fspiking prices, as others grapple to
OL,11,Fsave fuel and energy.
OL,13,FSince then, further damage has been
OL,14,Fcaused to key energy resources in the
OL,15,FMiddle East, with Qatar's massive Ras
OL,16,Fliquefied natural gas (LNG) facility
OL,17,Flosing 17% of its capacity in an
OL,18,FIranian strike, and a Kuwait oil
OL,19,Frefinery hit in a drone attack on
OL,20,FMarch 20.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
