OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Middle East supplied 60% of Asia's
OL,8,Fcrude oil imports in 2025.
OL,10,FPakistan's prime minister has
OL,11,Fimplemented a number of fuel-saving
OL,12,Fmeasures, including closing schools
OL,13,Ffor two weeks starting March 16,
OL,14,Fmoving government employees to a four-
OL,15,Fday week, and instructing 50% of
OL,16,Fgovernmental staff to start working
OL,17,Ffrom home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
