OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FGovernmental spending is also to be
OL,8,Fcut by 20%, while 60% of official
OL,9,Fvehicles, excluding ambulances and
OL,10,Fbuses, will be taken off the road,
OL,11,FShehbaz Sharif said on March 9.
OL,13,FUniversities in Pakistan and
OL,14,FBangladesh have closed their campuses
OL,15,Fand moved learning online.
OL,17,FBangladesh, which relies on imports
OL,18,Ffor around 95% of its energy, has
OL,19,Fencountered increased power cuts since
OL,20,Fthe war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
