OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIn the Philippines, government
OL,8,Fofficers have switched to a four-day
OL,9,Fweek, and office workers have been
OL,10,Ftold to switch computers off during
OL,11,Flunch breaks and keep air conditioning
OL,12,Ftemperatures beneath 24C.
OL,14,FOfficials in Thailand and Vietnam are
OL,15,Falso being encouraged to work from
OL,16,Fhome, with officials in Thailand
OL,17,Fencouraged to use stairs instead of
OL,18,Felevators and wear short-sleeved
OL,19,Fshirts to work to reduce the need for
OL,20,Fair-conditioning.
OL,26,@tD@XOX
