OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn Vietnam, domestic airlines could
OL,13,Fface fuel shortages from next month if
OL,14,Fthe conflict does not end, the Civil
OL,15,FAviation Authority of Vietnam said.
OL,17,FPetrochemical companies in Singapore
OL,18,Fand Indonesia have declared force
OL,19,Fmajeures over disruption to their
OL,20,Fsupply chains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
