OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSri Lanka has gone back to a QR-code
OL,8,Ffuel distribution system, last used
OL,9,Fduring its 2022 economic collapse, to
OL,10,Fmanage fuel stocks in the country,
OL,11,Fwith buses able to receive 60 litres
OL,12,Fand cars 15 litres.
OL,14,FA 24/7 tourism hotline has also been
OL,15,Fset up offering support to visitors
OL,16,Fimpacted by airspace closures in the
OL,17,FGulf region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
