OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSpain is reducing VAT on gasoline and
OL,8,Fdiesel from 21% to 10% and cutting a
OL,9,F5% tax on using electricity, as part
OL,10,Fof a wide-spanning E5 billion relief
OL,11,Fpackage announced by President Pedro
OL,12,FSanchez on Friday.
OL,14,FThe aim of the package is to support
OL,15,Faround 20 million households and 3
OL,16,Fmillion companies.
