OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FGreece has imposed price controls on
OL,8,Ffuel and household staples, such as
OL,9,Ffood, cleaning supplies and
OL,10,Ftoiletries, with the measures set to
OL,11,Ftake effect until June 30, a
OL,12,Fgovernment spokesman said.
OL,14,FIn the UK, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,15,Fsaid the government may issue energy
OL,16,Fsupport packages if the cost of fuel
OL,17,Fand energy does not decrease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
