OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Nothing is off the table at this
OL,8,Fstage. We are looking at targeted
OL,9,Fsupport as well as broader measures
OL,10,Fbut it is just too early to say what
OL,11,Fis needed," Reeves told the Treasury
OL,12,Fselect committee.
OL,14,FHungary has placed a ban on the export
OL,15,Fof oil, petrol and diesel, and
OL,16,Finstated a cap on fuel prices, economy
OL,17,Fminister Marton Nagy said in a
OL,18,FFacebook post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
