OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSweden-based airline SAS said it was
OL,8,Ftemporarily increasing its fare prices
OL,9,Fto adjust to the rise in jet fuel
OL,10,Fcosts.
OL,12,FLast week Russian President Vladimir
OL,13,FPutin said his country - the second-
OL,14,Flargest oil exporter in the world -
OL,15,Fwas was willing to work with European
OL,16,Fcustomers again, if they required.
OL,18,FMany European countries have sharply
OL,19,Freduced their reliance on Russian oil
OL,20,Fand gas since 2022, when Putin invaded
OL,21,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
