OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAir New Zealand announced on March 12
OL,8,Fit would be cancelling 1,100 flights
OL,9,Funtil early May due to increases in
OL,10,Fjet fuel prices.
OL,12,FThe airline is also raising its prices
OL,13,Fon routes still operating, and said it
OL,14,Fmay need to take further action if the
OL,15,Fsituation does not improve.
OL,17,FOfficials in the country have also
OL,18,Fsaid they are considering invoking
OL,19,Femergency powers that could limit how
OL,20,Foften people are allowed to drive
OL,21,Fduring the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
