OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FWhen last used - following the Iranian
OL,8,Frevolution in 1979 - car owners had to
OL,9,Fnominate one day a week they wouldn't
OL,10,Fdrive and could face a fine if they
OL,11,Fbroke the rules.
OL,13,FAuthorities were also able to restrict
OL,14,Fthe sale of fuel through coupon-usage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
