OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAustralia announced plans to
OL,8,Ftemporarily relax petrol standards to
OL,9,Fallow for a "dirty" fuel, with higher
OL,10,Fsulphur levels, to be mixed in with
OL,11,Fcurrent supply, adding an extra 100
OL,12,Fmillion litres into the system a month
OL,13,Ffor 60 days.
OL,15,FSulfur is usually removed from petrol
OL,16,Fduring the refining process to reduce
OL,17,Fair pollution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
