OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIn Egypt, the government said it was
OL,8,Flimiting non-essential travel and
OL,9,Frationing street lighting, as fuel
OL,10,Fprices rose by 30% last week.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a press conference, Prime
OL,13,FMinister Moustafa Madbouli said a
OL,14,Fcrisis committee had been formed to
OL,15,Fmonitor the situation, noting that the
OL,16,Fdisruption to supply chains had
OL,17,F"affected many goods and services".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
