OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world adapting during Iran oil
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSouth Africa's FlySafair has
OL,8,Fintroduced a temporary fuel surcharge
OL,9,Fon bookings made between March 12 and
OL,10,FMay 12 due to rising costs.
OL,12,FAnalysts have warned that countries
OL,13,Flike Sudan, The Gambia, Central
OL,14,FAfrican Republic, Lesotho and
OL,15,FZimbabwe, which operate under
OL,16,Fprogrammes from the International
OL,17,FMonetary Fund could struggle as the
OL,18,Fcost of importing energy and fuel
OL,19,Fdrains their limited foreign exchange
OL,20,Freserves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
